Dialogs.Dialog: That's out of the blue. I'll buy one somewhere.
I have a sudden craving for donuts. I don't want the donuts from the store, I want the ones from the wagon.
Wagon... you mean a mobile market？
Yes, it's been the talk of the town lately. I wanted to try one when I heard about it.
Hmmm, where can I get one？
If I knew that, you would not have any trouble at all. Like finding a ghost.
(Oh, is that the rumored donut shop？)
This is the wagon donut shop we were talking about the other day, right？
Mmm, this smell I've been dreaming about. Go buy some！
Don't you just want a crepe every once in a while？
Crepes, huh... Yes, it may be a thinking about it, but it's exciting to eat it once in a while.
I know, right？ It's also good that it can handle everything from sweet desserts to side dishes like tuna.
Come to think of it, I heard that there is a mobile crepe vendor coming to this town recently.
Oh, Rinko has heard about it too. But... it's said that they always sell in different places, so it's hard to know where they are.
Well, I'll look for it next time. If I find it, let's eat together.
(Oh, is that the crepe shop I've heard so much about？)
There you are. Come on, look at that store.
Huh, this is the crepe shop I've heard so much about.
I found it by accident. I told you before we'd eat together, right？
Hehe, you remembered... Smells really good.
Let's buy one and eat at once.
Yup！ I wonder which flavor I should try...
It's so hot... Why is it so hot？ Hey, can I kick you？
You know, it could be scorching. It's the weather in Japan that's bad！
Then maybe you'd feel more relaxed if you had some ice cream, right？
That's true too... Oh, by the way, a girl in my class found a new gelato shop. She was talking about it.
Heh, you want to go buy one now？
It's a mobile wagon store, so you'll get tired just looking for it...
I see. Well, I'll let you know when I find it.
Thanks in advance. That's the thing, we have to do something about this heat now too...
(Oh, is that the rumored gelato shop？)
Hey, that's the gelato shop we were talking about the other day, ▲小早川＊▲！
For real. You've been looking for it？
Thanks for remembering what Rinko said... Hehe.
Let's eat together. What flavor do you want？
I want to eat delicious sweet chestnuts.
It's fall, after all！ But why, all of a sudden？
The sweet chestnuts I had yesterday weren't very good... Well, I ate them all.
That's too bad... Well, I heard rumors of delicious sweet chestnuts sold by mobile vendors.
That's the thing, they don't have a specific place and time. So it seems rare.
Hey, if I hear something like that, it makes me want to eat even more.
Hmm. Well, I guess I'll take a look...
(Oh, is that the rumored sweet chestnut shop？)
These are... chestnuts！？ Did you go out of your way to buy them？
Thanks. I'm glad I can eat them, though....
I'm glad you remembered our conversation and really looked out for me.
Ah, nevermind. I just heard there's a baked sweet potato shop that's been popping up around lately.
Popping up？ Why is that a rumor？
They're delicious, but you never know when or where they'll show up. It's a legendary baked sweet potato.
Hey, when you find it, tell Rinko about it.
Yeah, I'll have to look for it.
(Oh, is that the rumored baked sweet potato shop？)
Look, I found the baked sweet potato shop we were talking about before.
Ah, it's true. I like it. It's like a winter tradition, isn't it？
Can't wait to try them. Freshly and crunchy baked sweet potatoes！ I hope it's sweet and crunchy... Hehe.
I'm starting to look forward to it.
If it's good, I'll buy some to take back home.
Hey, hey, did you hear about that？
I heard that some of the students saw a UFO at the same time.
Oh, I might have heard that.
Why doesn't it show up in front of Rinko...
Huh, you want to see it？
I'm not saying that's the case... but I'd like to get some kind of proof, wouldn't you？
I'll see if I can get a picture of it.
What？ Why are you in a panic？
Don't mind that, check this out.
A photo？ ...Oh, you don't think it's a UFO？ You caught it perfectly.
Haha, I knew you wanted to see it.
That's... well, I don't mind. Hehe.
Hey, do you know about Towassy？
Towassy... I think I've heard of it, or maybe not.
It's a legendary giant creature that lives in Lake Towano.
So, you know, go find Towassy and take its picture.
Because it sounds fun, but it's a lot of work. Rinko is not good at waiting for something for a long time.
Hmm, well, I'll look for it in moderation.
I got what you've been waiting for, ▲小早川＊▲！
The one I've been waiting for？ ...What？
Hey, did you forget the Towassy search party？
Ah, you meant that. Then... that means you got it...
Yes, photos！ I managed to get its picture.
Really... Is this real？ Did you take this？ What did it look like？
Now, be patient. I'll take my time answering your questions.
Don't waste your time and hurry up and talk. I have so many questions I want to ask you.
It's almost time for final exams...
Hah... that's a pain in the ass. Are you studying for the exams？
Well... that's I wanted to ask you too.
Hmmm, I'm getting ready for it... So where are you aiming for then？
Hah... it's time for final exams...
Tests are such a hassle, whose idea was it？ I'm not motivated at all...
Wouldn't it be a little more motivating if you set some goals？
You said it like it's someone else's business. Are you okay？
You're confident？ Then what's your goal？
No way... you shouldn't be too hard on yourself, okay？
That's a very big thing to say.
You're good at jokes, aren't you？
I'm not trying to make a joke...
Amazing！ You set your sights high, didn't you？
Heh... why not？ It's not like you have to stretch too far.
I'll keep my feet on the ground.
Yeah, I'm sure you'll be fine.
Right, well, that's how it is.
Anyway, now that we have a goal, let's do our best.
Geez, don't change your goals now.
I know. I'll do my best！
I hope you can achieve your goal. Good luck to both of us.
I think I did pretty good.
Hmm. Well, don't let your guard down tomorrow.
Heh. Well, anyway, let's keep our spirits up for tomorrow.
I see. Let's work hard again tomorrow.
Anyway, good job for the week.
It's been a long week... Well, I'm glad it's all over.
We both worked hard this past week. Good job！
That's what Rinko would say. Anyway, congrats...
Yes, yes, what a nice joke.
Yay！ I didn't expect first place！
Thanks. I feel like I'm dreaming...
Well, Rinko believed in you... Hehe.
Well, you know, this is what happens when you get a little serious.
Then next time, get more serious and aim for first place.
Oh！ I'm in the top ten.
Hmm, I knew you could do it. Congrats.
Don't get carried away. Next time, you'll win first place.
So now you'll aim for the first place, right？ Good luck... Hehe.
I managed to make it safely into the top 100.
You have to clear at least this much. As Rinko's boyfriend.
Thank goodness I made it into the top 100.
Hmm, you achieved your goal. Congratulations.
Well, it's a man's ironclad rule to do what he says, isn't it？ Why don't you set a higher goal next time？
Whew... It ranked in the top 100.
I'm glad you achieved your goal.
The first place was not possible...
Well, you made the effort. It's okay.
Yes, it's meaningful to have strived for the first place.
...It was reckless to aim for the first place.
What are you depressed about？ Why don't you just try again next time？
Yeah. The tests will come again, even if you don't want it to.
I knew it couldn't be first place...
Yeah... I guess that was a reckless goal.
That's not true... Good luck next time. You'll be fine！
Too bad I didn't make it to the top 10.
I see... but I know you've been working hard.
Cheer up. It's not the end of the world.
Instead, you'll get your revenge next time, I promise！
Ah... I guess I didn't get into the top 10...
Sorry to hear that. But it was cool to see you doing your best... maybe. Hehe.
So cheer up and let's do our best again.
Guh... I'm not in the top 100.
Ah, your goal was not achieved.
Well, I was so confident about it...
That confidence can make you careless.
Hah... I didn't even get into the top 100.
It was a shame. Well, it was close, wasn't it？
If you take the plunge and aim for the top 10 or so, the top 100 might be a piece of cake.
Guh... really... I'm not even it the top 100...
Hmm... I was rooting for you.
This was a lack of effort. I admit it.
Anyway, this really is the end of all exams！
Let's change the mood and have some fun.
Yeah. We should have a date.
In the meantime, it's almost time for the fun- filled summer vacation♪
Yeah. Let's change the mood and make lots of memories.
When the tests are over, it's already the end of the year. Winter vacation is coming soon.
It's true. Let's enjoy it to the fullest.
Yes, it's called "The Ghost of Towano Castle".
Or perhaps it is more of an urban legend...
Recently, strange moaning noises can be heard at night at Towano Castle. It's not so unusual.
Hmm... maybe it's part of the castle's atmosphere.
Yes. Maybe it's too early to tell, but you can at least get a feel of the atmosphere.
It's decided. Come on, let's go！
Now... I wonder where it is...
It's a castle, but it's a big place. It's hard to go around...
...When you think about it, this a pain in the ass.
Can't you hear it？ Faint moaning.
Okay, let's go then. Because my boyfriend is scared.
I wonder what that thing was...
Remember, it's the "The Ghost of Towano Castle".
What, are you okay with that？
If you know you're going to see it, then you won't be afraid, you know.
This is where you heard the voices before.
Well, maybe I was just hearing things in my head. Maybe it was some kind of animal.
Well, maybe that was it. We're wasting time if we stay too long, so let's go.
(It's actually a silly story, and it's better to keep silent so you don't get disappointed.)
I haven't heard any particular rumors.
Then I'll tell you. It's "The Legend of Dracula's Mansion".
No, I mean, real-life rumors. It's been all over the news lately.
There's a Western-style house in this town where satanic rituals may or may not take place at night...
It's a rumor... So let's get this straight, okay？
The ritual is at night, isn't it too early to start now？
It's the hunter's job to do something about that.
What do you mean with hunter...
It's just... I heard a sound...
And now, we made it clear.
Speaking of which, I wonder if the rumors, were true...
The rumor about "The Legend of Dracula's Mansion".
I'm still curious, so can we go back？
Don't worry, you've Rinko with you.
Why not, the devil's on holiday？
Maybe. Or maybe I misheard something.
Well, that can't be an actual satanic ritual, but I was hoping for a little more.
In fact, that's how it's like.
Hmm, well, I guess we've killed some time. Let's go.
(I could tell you the truth, but I'll just shut up.)
Oh, did you see the news yesterday？ You know, that one.
"Bigfoot deep in the mountains", of course.
Bigfoot？ Is that what you call UMA？
That's an unidentified animal. Footprints were spotted in the mountains.
It seems so. They haven't found the actual Bigfoot yet.
If it had been discovered, it would have been a bigger deal.
Between you and me, I heard there's even a prize for finding it.
What do you say, bounty hunter？
Me？ Will you help me ▲小早川＊▲？
...No way. It's a pain in the ass and there's no way they're really there.
So, you know, to pass the time, you should look for it.
Hmm, what are you talking about？
Ah, the "Bigfoot deep in the mountains" we talked about before.
It was someone's prank after all.
Even for pranks, I wish they were more refined.
It's not like it bothers anyone, so it's all about the entertainment.
It seems there were a lot of people who took it seriously.
Good grief. But, well, those people had a good time, didn't they？
Hah, I wonder if there is anything else interesting to do...
(I should tell her what I saw, but I better keep quiet...)
Do you want to hear what Rinko has been stocking up on？
Do you know "Ghosts of the Valley"？
I don't know of any ghost stories...
I hear it's quite a hot topic right now.
They say a ghost of a woman who has left this world behind in the valley of Oku-Towano...
Heh, if it's a hot topic, that means it can be witnessed.
It seems so. It's a common story, but when it's so close to you, it's a little exciting, isn't it？
Yes, it is. Better a minor ghost near you than a major ghost far away.
You mentioned "The Ghosts of the Valley" before.
What, are you tired of it？
Well, there was no new information. What's up？
Well, I actually got this email...
That's pretty elaborate for a prank.
I was pretty seriously surprised when it first arrived.
...Hey, why did it come to you？
Hmmm, I wonder if anyone else received this. It's a local ghost, so it's not exactly a random email...
(Well, it looks like you found it interesting...)
You know, we went to an amusement park before.
My favorite cat key-chain. I didn't realize it at the time.
I see... Did you notify the amusement park？
Shouldn't you do it sooner rather than later？ I know it's your favorite.
I hear they go around the park at night picking up lost and found items.
But that's not all. They say that anything that is picked up by the ghost will be cursed unless you take it back directly.
So that's the reason why you're hesitating...
I'm not afraid of curses, but... it's kind of vexing knowing you've lost something.
But how are you going to find it？ We can't get in.
I'm just kidding. If I'm honest, I'd like to be let in.
I'm glad you're a man who knows what he's talking about. Now you can look for it.
I guess so. Let's look for it before it gets too late.
It's dark... time to give up？
What are you guys doing here at this hour？ The park has been closed for a long time.
Ah, a cat key chain. There it is.
Mm-hmm. Um, thank you very much.
Don't mention it. Still... it's a hassle to change clothes, so I was just going to keep going and look around after the park closed, but I didn't know that was the rumor.
I don't want to bother you, so from now on I'll change my clothes first. Then, go home as soon as possible.
Hehe, you were scared at first.
You were first, weren't you ▲小早川＊▲？
Haha. Well, it's getting late, so let's go home.
I'm glad we came, but... I wonder if we can go in.
I dunno. I can't just go in there without permission... I wonder if there are any security people there. Let's see if we can find him.
There doesn't seem to be anyone here. I guess I'll give up today.
It's not always picked up by ghosts. Let's go to the information desk and ask if anyone has reported any lost property.
A cat key-chain... hasn't been delivered. Apologies.
Don't worry, thank you very much.
It wasn't there... we should give up for today.
